title: Swing Your Sword | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Swing Your Sword | Joel Osteen
description:
If you want to see God’s power at work in your life, you have to do your part to fight the forces that are trying to keep you from your destiny. Start declaring what God promised. When you speak His Word over your situation, that's you swinging your sword.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
